    "body": "Stage.fetch does not set the 'expand' kwarg for mirror URL fetchers so when retrieving a resource which should not be expanded from a mirror it will fail.\n\nFor an example see conversation at https://github.com/LLNL/spack/pull/1233\n\nIn summary: the spack cache is a mirror so this can be created simply by installing, uninstalling, and attempting to reinstall (which triggers the error).\n",
